HEADWORD: Septembrist
<hw>Sep*tem"brist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>septembriste</ets>.]</ety> <def>An agent in the massacres in Paris,
committed in patriotic frenzy, on the 22d of September, 1792.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

